      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) directly correspond to ASTM F1717 performance metrics used in regulatory submission.",
      "rationale": "The three QoIs — construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement — are the primary performance metrics specified in ASTM F1717 and are the quantities reported in the regulatory submission. Relevance of QoIs to the COU is fully established."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/factor/relevance-activities-001",
